Rating: 3
Like any good Thai-inspired recipe, this is a great blend of sweet and tangy. Especially considering how quick and easy it is, I will certainly be making it again. I would strongly suggest that everyone heed the suggestions to add 1/2 tsp of sesame oil as it really rounds out the dish. I am at a loss why those who panned this dish did so, especially those who didn't like the taste of fish sauce, as it is one of the principal flavours of Thai cuisine.

